### Auth Requests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "kishoyianbrianmwangi@gmail.com",
  "password": "pass123",
